00:11:54,042 --> 00:11:57,818
♪After the wind, lingering desires stay♪

197
00:11:59,610 --> 00:12:03,674
♪Clouds drift and shape, momentary play♪

198
00:12:05,114 --> 00:12:09,018
♪Emotions reach, stirring in the heart♪

199
00:12:10,458 --> 00:12:14,042
♪Tears in solitude,
how often they start♪

200
00:12:15,098 --> 00:12:18,042
♪The wind's whispering,
and rain's sobbing♪

201
00:12:18,042 --> 00:12:20,250
♪Years pass
with flowers' bloom and grace♪

202
